127
00:06:12.583 --> 00:06:14.464
-FRANKLIN: Sonja. Sales.
-Nice to meet you. Mr. Preston.

128
00:06:14.523 --> 00:06:17.203
-Mmm.
-And finally. Sierra. Marketing.

129
00:06:17.228 --> 00:06:18.430
All right. sit down.
sit down. sit down.

130
00:06:18.455 --> 00:06:19.723
